
System Requirements
===================

* Java SE JDK 5 or greater (http://java.sun.com/)
* Ant 1.7 or greater (http://ant.apache.org/)


Building Pivot
==============

* To compile all Pivot source files into binary class files:

  $ ant

* To regenerate the JAR files in the lib folder:

  $ ant package

* To generate Javadoc

  $ ant doc

* To generate the Pivot distribution

  $ ant dist
